 <table>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tbody>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">MPN:</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">MCN</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">UPC:</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">21563440324</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">Features:</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">Dry off quickly while camping or swimming with this super absorbent microfiber towel; the attached snap loop lets you easily hang it for fast drying whether at camp or at home</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">This microfiber bath towel is compact and lightweight, packing up to the size of a water bottle and weighing under 12 oz; make it your go-to towel for hiking or backpacking</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">Stay fresh longer between washes with an antimicrobial treatment that inhibits the growth of odor-causing bacteria and fungi; use it for sports, fitness, yoga, and exercise</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">Pack in the dual-pocket storage bag, along with your toiletries or sunscreen, and bring it camping, backpacking, hiking, or to the beach, pool, or gym</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">Packaging may vary</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t  </table>\n\t\t\t  </div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t  </div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t  <div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t  <p>© 2026</p></div></div>",
